spec_data.Name: soci-odbc-devel
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the Odbc back-end for soci, i.e., header
files and dynamic libraries specific to the Odbc database. If you
would like to develop programs using soci and Odbc, you will need
to install soci-odbc.
